Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.15,0:01:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八話\N新的戰鬥\N闖進來的謎樣美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次就拜託你了劍心\N接下的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五。六的半！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了是勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二四的丁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了!我贏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之兄今天運氣好像不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛剛就一直輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！我特意的期待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流的讀法怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全中不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.39,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是勝負\N劍術的讀法是完全不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.43,0:02:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我說有重要的事要我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助賭博是法律所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.50,0:02:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的賭博也只是好朋友們\N用零用錢在賭的快樂遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且大家\N也是從以前就開始接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是情投意合的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是人品不太好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.78,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一句是多餘的左之兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼看最壞的不就是左之兄嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是笑的時侯，下次再不中的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會輕易放過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎？劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.17,0:03:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！在那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二。六的丁！二。六的丁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分勝負吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二。六的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二。五的半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又贏了！！又贏了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是喝茶的時侯劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是偶然也好，給我中一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼說也。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之兄今天非常的全神貫注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.74,0:03:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然的！\N我跟賣糖果的宵太借了一點錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我想加上利息\N錢要還給他才來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼宵太那傢伙在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要聽到是賭博一定會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宵太。。死了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.33,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼生病嗎\N那麼有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健康的傢伙不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。。。鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道是從誰那得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是對身體有好處而被慫恿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現是鴉片的時侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宵太那傢伙已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.16,0:04:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪裏的傢伙給宵太鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被壞人追殺著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你！救救我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.31,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿惠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經逃不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是你們這些混帳嗎\N你們要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉嗦！我們有事找那女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少插嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在非常的生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要注意說話的口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做這種事認為這樣就算了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.44,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是觀柳先生的私家護衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你們要注意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是武田觀柳的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是左之兄\N對方可是壞東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武田觀柳。。。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.68,0:05:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面是青年實業家\N實際上卻擁有數十萬的護衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說在從事非常不好的買賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟那傢伙是什麼關係？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也不知道，真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以胡說的高荷惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.87,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼時候來的？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝作惹人憐的女人\N讓人家同情你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一隻女狐貍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是只有兩個人監視你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我米子見也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了我就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去跟觀柳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不論做什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要逃出去給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太可愛了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為你能逃出去嗎？特別是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀次！阿知！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就不是嚇唬你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個螺旋鏢射兩腳\N這樣就可處置掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是很瞭解實情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生對於惡作劇而傷人之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最看不過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口！這次輪到你了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我們的同伴。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.32,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了\N劍心這傢伙一定贏了不少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼\N到賭場去玩就是一件不好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來後。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會就這樣放過他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,。。啊。。好像要下血雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛！很高興的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難懂的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來晚了真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.74,0:07:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常老舊的家\N是劍術道場嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！這位是高荷惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠小姐被壞人追殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那時侯劍哥哥救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。。劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許真的太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對救來的女人有意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以連劍心\N都不能把她丟著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不。不是這樣的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又是怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。是因為。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候的劍哥哥真的非常的帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太髒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛一副色迷迷的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我錯看你了劍心你這笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太嚇人了粗暴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧劍哥哥。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.39,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餵你到底跟我們的劍心\N有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥是救了我的最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又是劍哥哥的什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.81,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看不是戀人\N有汗臭味的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不是劍哥哥喜歡的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是對不起\N你說汗臭味的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜一點阿熏\N什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再嘲弄她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位小姐可是非常的純情單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那位女狐貍可不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起那位粗暴的姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.83,0:09:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比較重要吧劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.15,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要！救救我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你，下次不會再失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求求你！讓我們逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論什麼事都做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是實業家的性格嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於沒用的人不馬上排除的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心裏就不舒暢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這點老大忍耐力就比較強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米子見的老大始終是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於多餘的話要謹慎一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.38,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然明白\N反正我只要小惠能回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒有任何的意見。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若，高荷惠人在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在鎮裏的一間道場裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！你跟火男\N去幫米子見的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.77,0:10:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了米子見，再失敗的話\N就不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會銘記在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了，老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何\N那重要的下金蛋的雌鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是絕對不會放手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳的私人護衛大約有六十人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是最可怕的是老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟私人護衛不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是原隱密者束縛著\N御庭番眾的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治維新之前年齡才十五歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.36,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就成為江戶城警護\N御庭番眾老大的天才隱密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四之森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是能跟劍哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙即使來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也安心了。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼那又是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御許庭番眾真的出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人再怎麼厲害也沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏再住下去也沒用了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼小惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.86,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠小姐為什麼\N從觀柳那裏逃出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.06,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且觀柳為什麼\N會對小惠窮追不捨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家在說話要聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去探索女人的過去真是庸俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是關鍵問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷聽不太好吧。小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活心流的老師會哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.10,0:12:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心一回來\N兩人就關在房間裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐你應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.17,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心這傢伙劍術是很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是對人卻沒有辦法\N特別是女人跟小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道。可是。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.31,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許對人有太過喜歡的程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！沒有什麼\N劍心大概沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.42,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是不行的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助有異常嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方有御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他們已經都知道\N我們這裏的所有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心一點是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是忍者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙不會這樣就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想增加你的麻煩。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.22,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是或許會引起\N一，二個騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.02,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小熏小姐\N小生一定會保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到了劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有騷動嗎？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.30,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.64,0:13:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了不讓我參興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是劍心組的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心組？那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管拿劍或鐵炮來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是跟什麼人為敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明神禰彥都會跟他打下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子還這麼的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你跟那些傢伙解決掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了禰彥。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的忽然起內訌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心組真是前途多難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖的把阿惠交出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我就會手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是御廷番眾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對。御庭番眾的其中一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男就是指我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼誰是我的對手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是你們兩個一起上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好。。好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有力氣的自傲大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。這裏交給我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之對方是御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是只靠力氣的話。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管什麼都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不打算保護那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是被招惹的想打架而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼對自己的力量有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不中的話就沒有意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險！你這章魚混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯，能躲過必殺的火炎吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是接下來就不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是御庭番眾\N最會使用的火術的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.69,0:15:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男原來的漢字\N是這麼寫的所以才這麼念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙沒有不能燒的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一大把年紀了不要玩火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說玩火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耍這麼小的花招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生的頭髮一根也沒辦法燒掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就從你開始燒起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋東西那樣就能中斷激戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耍小花招的是誰\N我讓你嘗嘗看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男的跟之前的米子見\N是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼樣也贏不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心為了你在戰鬥著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你就這樣逃走了\N太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.85,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾是認為\N殺人沒有什麼的團體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是女人也不會饒了她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也許也會被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是如何強的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心是一定會保護我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不是那種毀約的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五升的油也。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火的遊戲已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說這傢伙交給我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的幫助，可是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我重擺架勢，耐打的我\N這點傷只要用唾液就能治好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,油已經補充好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了章魚混蛋在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定要讓你嘗嘗火刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極大火炎吐息！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定沒辦法避開了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,判斷得很好與其一味的閃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如攻擊來得容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受傷也能減少到最低的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是變戲法的窮門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦呢？竅門已經沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝負還沒有結束呢。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕而易舉的勝了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相反的滿身創痍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害。。。不簡單。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人到底是何人物。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我最值得驕傲。。。的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個都不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！太恐怖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺真的贏得很辛苦的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.07,0:18:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！火男這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕而易舉的就被收拾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不是又失敗了嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話那女人。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.46,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道武田觀柳\N為何會對這女人那麼執著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.36,0:18:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙讓我變成這樣。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我也是劍心組的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好好表現一下怎麼可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逞強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先讓我看一下傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一點擦。。。傷。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰。。禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好管閒事了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小孩只有一個小時的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒殺螺旋鏢！這是御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米子見最厲害的必殺絕技！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你們全都收拾掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先從劍客混蛋開始。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.18,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時代\N還有像你這樣的劍客存在。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.89,0:19:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點太小看對手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲早要跟你戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時侯再分出勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.24,0:19:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正先把毒吸出來再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼！不要妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從傷口吸出毒素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造成細菌感染反而不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開！這不是\N外行人該出場的時侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.52,0:20:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發燒昏睡。有點痛苦\N瞳孔放大。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是曼陀羅藥的毒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐我把需要的藥寫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到醫生那裏去拿藥來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥去煮熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有準備擦手巾\N及在家裏的藥品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纏頭巾的你到賣冰的店\N把所有冰都買來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在發什麼呆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解毒可是有時間性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是。。是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥加油我不准你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現是鴉片的時侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宵太那傢伙已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這傢伙會有鴉片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.86,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心的也許是這女人

